{"pageProps":{"note":{"id":"lmrnaqmwrgfu2drm93lkdj4","title":"Current Tools","desc":"","updated":1777538049425,"created":1777536861087,"custom":{},"fname":"random-markov-field.mass-spectrometry.current-tools","type":"note","vault":{"fsPath":".","selfContained":true,"name":"acol-dws"},"contentHash":"ce9c533dbecf70d0c18a4d593ee75581","links":[],"anchors":{"current-tools":{"type":"header","text":"Current tools","value":"current-tools","line":8,"column":0,"depth":1},"ms2---smiles-de-novo":{"type":"header","text":"MS2 -> SMILES (de novo)","value":"ms2---smiles-de-novo","line":9,"column":0,"depth":2},"ms2---smiles-database-lookup-ie-check-a-list-of-smiles":{"type":"header","text":"MS2 -> SMILES (database lookup i.e. check a list of SMILES)","value":"ms2---smiles-database-lookup-ie-check-a-list-of-smiles","line":14,"column":0,"depth":2},"smiles---ms2-mass-spectrum-simulation":{"type":"header","text":"SMILES -> MS2 (mass spectrum simulation)","value":"smiles---ms2-mass-spectrum-simulation","line":20,"column":0,"depth":2},"needs":{"type":"header","text":"Needs","value":"needs","line":27,"column":0,"depth":1}},"children":[],"parent":"y0pxs489vqcic0zne2qqmbc","data":{}},"body":"<h1 id=\"current-tools\">Current Tools<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#current-tools\"></a></h1>\n<h1 id=\"current-tools-1\">Current tools<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#current-tools-1\"></a></h1>\n<h2 id=\"ms2---smiles-de-novo\">MS2 -> SMILES (de novo)<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#ms2---smiles-de-novo\"></a></h2>\n<ul>\n<li>DiffMS : <a href=\"https://doi.org/10.48550/arXiv.2502.09571\">https://doi.org/10.48550/arXiv.2502.09571</a></li>\n<li>MADGEN : <a href=\"https://arxiv.org/pdf/2501.01950\">https://arxiv.org/pdf/2501.01950</a></li>\n<li>MSNovelist : <a href=\"https://www.nature.com/articles/s41592-022-01486-3\">https://www.nature.com/articles/s41592-022-01486-3</a></li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"ms2---smiles-database-lookup-ie-check-a-list-of-smiles\">MS2 -> SMILES (database lookup <em>i.e.</em> check a list of SMILES)<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#ms2---smiles-database-lookup-ie-check-a-list-of-smiles\"></a></h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Sirius</li>\n<li>Metfrag</li>\n<li>JESTR : <a href=\"https://arxiv.org/pdf/2411.14464\">https://arxiv.org/pdf/2411.14464</a></li>\n<li>MIST-CF : <a href=\"https://pubs.acs.org/doi/full/10.1021/acs.jcim.3c01082\">https://pubs.acs.org/doi/full/10.1021/acs.jcim.3c01082</a></li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"smiles---ms2-mass-spectrum-simulation\">SMILES -> MS2 (mass spectrum simulation)<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#smiles---ms2-mass-spectrum-simulation\"></a></h2>\n<ul>\n<li>CFM-ID</li>\n<li>ICEBERG : <a href=\"https://www.biorxiv.org/content/10.1101/2025.05.28.656653v2\">https://www.biorxiv.org/content/10.1101/2025.05.28.656653v2</a></li>\n<li>FraGNNet : <a href=\"https://arxiv.org/abs/2404.02360\">https://arxiv.org/abs/2404.02360</a></li>\n<li>FIORA : <a href=\"https://www.nature.com/articles/s41467-025-57422-4\">https://www.nature.com/articles/s41467-025-57422-4</a></li>\n</ul>\n<h1 id=\"needs\">Needs<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#needs\"></a></h1>\n<p>For the MRF, I need a tool that can output a probability between a spectrum and a SMILES.</p>","noteIndex":{"id":"3rbfqqbp7pwbkdcrgc97u7l","title":"Anticipated Chemistry of Life","desc":"","updated":1727785927929,"created":1671985562294,"custom":{"nav_order":0,"permalink":"/"},"fname":"root","type":"note","vault":{"fsPath":".","selfContained":true,"name":"acol-dws"},"contentHash":"f1947bd87c177e8ee5739c542c5dc574","links":[],"anchors":{"welcome-to-the-dendron-of-the-anticipated-chemistry-of-life":{"type":"header","text":"Welcome to the Dendron of the Anticipated Chemistry of Life","value":"welcome-to-the-dendron-of-the-anticipated-chemistry-of-life","line":8,"column":0,"depth":1}},"children":["l03fwlci5f5rdpot3v7oli6","zxc3pre92d542wg70hmdhgl","yl3j0gor5m5od4j1y5vbxih","jqc7nvrtk6bmno394fcuw1u","ghtzzi5buglirob2qidl5eo","9k3x188zfa3yookx15exx47","5h5hzto7ygkv874tw74ywks"],"parent":null,"data":{},"body":"\n# Welcome to the Dendron of the Anticipated Chemistry of Life\n\nThis dendron has the purpose to serve as a laboratory notebook for my PhD thesis. It will contain all the notes that I will take during my research as well as some results of the experiments and models that I will develop and test.\n"},"collectionChildren":null,"customHeadContent":null,"config":{"version":5,"dev":{"enablePreviewV2":true,"enableSelfContainedVaults":true},"commands":{"lookup":{"note":{"selectionMode":"extract","confirmVaultOnCreate":true,"vaultSelectionModeOnCreate":"smart","leaveTrace":false,"bubbleUpCreateNew":true,"fuzzThreshold":0.2}},"randomNote":{},"insertNoteLink":{"aliasMode":"none","enableMultiSelect":false},"insertNoteIndex":{"enableMarker":false},"copyNoteLink":{"aliasMode":"title"},"templateHierarchy":"template"},"workspace":{"vaults":[{"fsPath":".","selfContained":true,"name":"acol-dws"}],"journal":{"dailyDomain":"daily","name":"journal","dateFormat":"y.MM.dd","addBehavior":"childOfDomain"},"scratch":{"name":"scratch","dateFormat":"y.MM.dd.HHmmss","addBehavior":"asOwnDomain"},"task":{"name":"task","dateFormat":"y.MM.dd","addBehavior":"asOwnDomain","statusSymbols":{"":" ","wip":"w","done":"x","assigned":"a","moved":"m","blocked":"b","delegated":"l","dropped":"d","pending":"y"},"taskCompleteStatus":["done","x"],"prioritySymbols":{"H":"high","M":"medium","L":"low"},"todoIntegration":false,"createTaskSelectionType":"selection2link"},"graph":{"zoomSpeed":1,"createStub":false},"enableAutoCreateOnDefinition":false,"enableXVaultWikiLink":false,"enableRemoteVaultInit":true,"enableUserTags":true,"enableHashTags":true,"workspaceVaultSyncMode":"noCommit","enableAutoFoldFrontmatter":false,"enableEditorDecorations":true,"maxPreviewsCached":10,"maxNoteLength":204800,"enableFullHierarc